data.description: Yes, you read that right- over FOUR Thousand square feet of flexible living space in this sprawling ranch home! Thoughtfully designed for accessibility: Ramps on Exterior, Brand New Wheelchair Lift System, Elevator, Track/Lift system, Shower and more.  Mid-Century Modern flare gives the home personality with a bright, open floorplan. On the main floor: Semi-Open Concept Great Room/Kitchen/Dining area, Sunroom, 3 large bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, first floor laundry. Lower Level: 2nd Full Kitchen, 3rd Full Bath, Bar, MASSIVE rec room, a 4th huge bedroom (Could easily make a 5th). All appliances stay, New Washer and Dryer, Updated Electrical, Central Air and more. This versatile home has the space and functionality for everyone to feel right at home! Conveniently located to all that Beautiful Warren Ohio has to offer! Minutes to Downtown, Trumbull Country Club, and highway access!
